The '''635 Group''' is a network of militant [[anti-fascism|anti-fascists]] operating in [[West Yorkshire]].<ref>{{cite book|last1=Vervaecke|first1=Philippe|title=À droite de la droite: Droites radicales en France et en Grande-Bretagne au XXe siècle|date=March 26, 2012|publisher=Presses Univ. Septentrion|isbn=2757403699|page=205}}</ref> Part of the Antifa movement of the 2000s, 635 Group was highly active in suppressing the [[British People's Party (2005)|British People's Party]] until its dissolution in 2013.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Testa|first1=M.|title=Militant Anti-Fascism: 100 Years of Resistance|date=2015|publisher=AK Press|isbn=9781849352031|pages=298-9}}</ref>
